{"tid":2122392,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"警世：skip leg day既Ching 唔好戴n95","createTime":"2020-07-24T03:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T03:39:50.000Z","uid":85882,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"60974397df8fc4b50a06adb318edd0cf081e0bcc","tid":2122392,"uid":85882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:29:41.000Z","msg":"頭先望到有位巨Ching 虎背熊腰，手瓜起展<br />\n頭戴n95，遠睇有個猛字刻喺額頭<br />\n諗住行開少少以免被處刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n誰不知一望落少少見到一對港女腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即刻霸氣盡失 上重下輕<br />\n再加埋個顯頭大既N95<br />\n成個行走的小雞咁<br />\n我當堂所有自信翻曬黎<br />\n同佢貼住膊頭咁行過<br />\n佢差啲比我雄壯既大腳震走<br />\n佢只能Dup低頭 望住我既股四頭悔恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e46cb8e747f830bfcfc357130e98ad0902f2f0","tid":2122392,"uid":85882,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:30:43.000Z","msg":"示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6kLSiZD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6kLSiZD.png&h=2161bf28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2dbd1e39fbe956d1a26fcce1241bfe6b9bbc9f0a","tid":2122392,"uid":4037,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f0e46cb8e747f830bfcfc357130e98ad0902f2f0","tid":2122392,"uid":85882,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:30:43.000Z","msg":"示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6kLSiZD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6kLSiZD.png&h=2161bf28&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:32:06.000Z","msg":"條撚又會生係塊面到咁有趣既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9838fb9f6246ea3a43e1521970c5e020c0bebafe","tid":2122392,"uid":85882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2dbd1e39fbe956d1a26fcce1241bfe6b9bbc9f0a"